Text: Due to the relatively low valuations in the healthcare space, namely the drug development companies of AbbVie (NYSE:ABBV), Gilead Sciences (NASDAQ:GILD), and Amgen (NASDAQ:AMGN), I have added to these positions and allowed the dividend income to slightly exceed the 20% limit.
